ation average of the coincident years with the peaks of this\ncycle. This comparison evidences a high statistical significance for the\nCenicaf\\'e, Naranjal and La Bella stations' series. Demonstrating the influence\nof the sunspot cycle in the regional precipitations. This result is useful in\nthe the long-term prevision of regional hydric availability.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 16 Dec 2015 23:37:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-12-18"}
